# happyr - "fitR, happyR"

Brings R's {styler} and {lintr} packages to the command line.

Make your R code fitR and happyR with the happyR cli tool.


## Installation

Install from PyPI:

```bash
# python3 -m pip install happyr
```


## Usage

```bash
happyr --help
```

To style with {styler}:

```bash
happyr style --help
```

To lint with {lintr}:

```bash
happyr lint --help
```



